              "name": "Opening Paragraph Two",
              "fill": "#374151",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "That is why the surfaces stay nearly white, the type does the heavy lifting, and the only moments of contrast are the ones that clarify direction.",
